{"id":1484,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":6,"title":"Conversation 6","subtitle":"Airport Check-in Frustrations","level":"B1","parts":9,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-6.1484/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-6-2024-08-18-22-42-01/0-conversation-6.mp3","transcript":"Whoa, check out that line!\nOnly one person working at the check-in counter,\nand it's going to take ages to get our luggage sorted.\nThey're definitely understaffed.\nWe should get priority boarding, or we might miss the flight.\nSounds like a plan, but I don't carry cash anymore.\nDo you think they take traveler's checks?\nNo worries, I got my credit card with me,\nit should work fine.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:59:35","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Whoa, check out that line!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-6-2024-08-18-22-42-01/1.mp3","time_start":0.31,"time_end":2.53},{"position":2,"content":"Only one person working at the check-in counter,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-6-2024-08-18-22-42-01/2.mp3","time_start":2.53,"time_end":5.2},{"position":3,"content":"and it's going to take ages to get our luggage sorted.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-6-2024-08-18-22-42-01/3.mp3","time_start":5.2,"time_end":8.18},{"position":4,"content":"They're definitely understaffed.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-6-2024-08-18-22-42-01/4.mp3","time_start":8.18,"time_end":10.3},{"position":5,"content":"We should get priority boarding, or we might miss the flight.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-6-2024-08-18-22-42-01/5.mp3","time_start":10.3,"time_end":13.37},{"position":6,"content":"Sounds like a plan, but I don't carry cash anymore.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-6-2024-08-18-22-42-01/6.mp3","time_start":13.37,"time_end":16.87},{"position":7,"content":"Do you think they take traveler's checks?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-6-2024-08-18-22-42-01/7.mp3","time_start":16.87,"time_end":19.14},{"position":8,"content":"No worries, I got my credit card with me,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-6-2024-08-18-22-42-01/8.mp3","time_start":19.14,"time_end":21.81},{"position":9,"content":"it should work fine.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-6-2024-08-18-22-42-01/9.mp3","time_start":21.81,"time_end":23.25}]}